Build Secure Research Workflow with Firefox Containers
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Install and configure Firefox Multi-Account Containers for OSINT research
Create dedicated containers for different research activities
Implement secure browsing practices using container isolation
Automate container management using Python scripts
Apply container-based workflows to real-world OSINT investigations
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of web browsers and internet navigation
Familiarity with Linux command line operations
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of OSINT fundamentals and privacy concepts
Lab Environment
Your cloud machine includes:

Ubuntu 22.04 LTS
