Task 1: Install and Configure Firefox Multi-Account Containers
Step 1.1: Install the Extension
Launch Firefox from the terminal:
firefox &
Navigate to about:addons in the address bar

Search for "Firefox Multi-Account Containers" and click Add to Firefox

Confirm installation and verify the container icon appears in the toolbar

